name: KaliMaPUNK
description:
DeathMONKpunk number 2!

The Divine Mother Kali is the destructive aspect of reality. She is the Daughter of Time and in time all material manifestations get destroyed. Worshipping Her is the worship of the transitory nature of Being. 

The cutting off of the Head symbolizes the cutting away of the Ego and Mind. You are not your transitory physical body. You are immutable Soul. 

Aum Ma Kring is a mantra to her beneficence!
